title: Extension: Wolfage Finance's new identity proposal
body:
Extending the proposal by 2 hours due to the misunderstanding caused by timezone. Read more about it [here](https://t.me/wolfagefinancecommunity/19312).

Proposing five logo choices for Wolfage Finance's new identity.

Requesting Wolfage Finance community members, who hold at least 1 WEFI in their wallet, to vote for their best choice among the five choices given.

The chosen identity will set the foundation for the whole Wolfage Finance's design system.

Note: All images are hosted on IPFS as well!
